## üó∫Ô∏è 12-Day Roadmap

| Day | Phase | Focus |
|----:|------|-------|
| **01** | Extraction | Structured outputs, JSON schemas, validation |
| **02** | Agency | Function calling & tool execution |
| **03** | Memory | Embeddings & vector database setup |
| **04** | Retrieval | RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) |
| **05** | Optimization | Prompt design & context management |
| **06** | Streaming | Token streaming & WebSocket handling |
| **07** | AWS Integration | Bedrock migration & Boto3 |
| **08** | Evaluation | Output testing & evaluation frameworks |
| **09** | Orchestration | LangChain / LlamaIndex foundations |
| **10** | Pipelines | Ingesting unstructured data (PDFs, Docs) |
| **11** | Deployment | Dockerized AI services & CI/CD |
| **12** | Final Build | ‚ÄúChat with My Docs‚Äù backend API |

---

## üìì Engineering Logs

### Day 01 ‚Äî The Structured Bridge

**Problem**  
Transforming unstructured human input into reliable machine-readable data.

**Key Learning**  
Schema-constrained outputs dramatically reduce downstream complexity.

**Implementation**
- Enforced structured responses using JSON schemas
- Eliminated fragile regex-based parsing

---

## üöÄ Setup & Execution

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.11+
- Docker
- AWS credentials (for Bedrock phases)

### Local Setup

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone <repo-url>
cd cosmonyx-ai-core

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
